### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/decolamos

### List Aircraft (Phase 0)
GET http://localhost:8080/aircraft

### Create Aircraft (Phase 0)
POST http://localhost:8080/aircraft
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "F-16C",
  "manufacturer": "Lockheed Martin"
}

### List AircraftV2 (Phase 0.5)
GET http://localhost:8080/aircraft-v2

### Create AircraftV2 — Full Payload
POST http://localhost:8080/aircraft-v2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "F-22A Raptor",
  "manufacturer": "Lockheed Martin",
  "serial_number": "LM-F22-001",
  "year_of_manufacture": 2005,
  "price_millions": "143.6",
