### Get AircraftV2 by ID (Replace UUID)
GET http://localhost:8080/aircraft-v2/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Update AircraftV2 (Replace UUID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/aircraft-v2/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "F-22B Raptor (Updated)",
  "manufacturer": "Lockheed Martin",
  "year_of_manufacture": 2010,
  "price_millions": "150.0",
  "empty_weight_kg": 19700.5,
  "status": "Maintenance",
  "role": "Fighter",
  "tags": ["stealth", "5th-gen", "updated"],
  "first_flight_date": "1997-09-07T00:00:00Z",
  "last_maintenance_time": "2026-01-01T10:00:00Z",
